no|b=no|q=Ravi Shankar|s=no|commons=Ravi Shankar|n=no|v=no|voy=no}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://www.ravishankar.org/|title=Ravi Shankar|publisher=Official website}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://eastmeetswestmusic.com/|title=East Meets West Music|publisher=Ravi Shankar Foundation}}\n* {{Allmusic|class=artist|id=p3434|label=Ravi Shankar}}\n* {{IMDb name|0788170|Ravi Shankar}}\n* [https://www.namm.org/library/oral-history/ravi-shankar Interview with Ravi Shankar] NAMM Oral History Library (2009)\n* [http://eastmeetswestmusic.com/discography/raga/ ''Raga'' (2010 Remaster) at East Meets West Music]\n\n{{Ravi Shankar}}\n{{navboxes\n|title=Navigation boxes related to Ravi Shankar\n|state=collapsed\n|list1=\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Awards\n|state=collapsed\n|list1=\n{{Bharat Ratna}}\n{{Padma Vibhushan Awards}}\n{{PadmaBhushanAwardRecipients 1960\u201369}}\n{{SangeetNatakAkademiFellowship}}\n{{RMA winners of India}}\n{{Polar Music Prize}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Family\n|state=collapsed\n|list1=\n{{Shankar family}}\n{{Anoushka Shankar}}\n{{Norah Jones}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title= Other associations\n|state=collapsed\n|list1=\n{{Woodstock}}\n{{George Harrison}}\n}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n{{good article}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Shankar, Ravi}}\n[[Category:1920 births]]\n[[Category:2012 deaths]]\n[[Category:All India Radio people]]\n[[Category:Angel Records artists]]\n[[Category:Apple Records artists]]\n[[Category:Articles containing video clips]]\n[[Category:Musicians from Varanasi]]\n[[Category:Bengali Hindus]]\n[[Category:Bengali people]]\n[[Category:Commandeurs of the L\u00e9gion d'honneur]]\n[[Category:Composers awarded knighthoods]]\n[[Category:Dark Horse Records artists]]\n[[Category:Deutsche Grammophon artists]]\n[[Category:EMI Classics and Virgin Classics artists]]\n[[Category:Fukuoka Asian Culture Prize winners]]\n[[Category:Grammy Award winners]]\n[[Category:Grammy Lifetime Achievement Award winners]]\n[[Category:Hindi film score composers]]\n[[Category:Hindustani instrumentalist